text: The 2014–15 USC Trojans women's basketball team represented University of Southern California during the 2014–15 NCAA Division I women's basketball season. The Trojans, led by second year head coach Cynthia Cooper-Dyke, played their home games at the Galen Center as members of the Pac-12 Conference. They finished the season 15–15, 7–11 in Pac-12 play to finish in a tie for seventh place.
